    {
      "role": "user",
      "content": "<|channel>thought\n<channel|>it's just not that simple. \"friends\" and \"family\" ... they all saw the headlines. they saw what they said about me. i can see the pity in their eyes or just the pure disgust. i can't go back to that life. there is no \"next step\" when the ground you're standing on doesn't even exist anymore. it feels like a logical conclusion, you know? like the version of me that mattered is just permanently deleted.",
